### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api

### 1. Successful Transfer (Alice to Bob)
POST {{baseUrl}}/transfer
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "senderId": 1,
    "recipientId": 2,
    "amount": 100
}

### 2. Edge Case: Insufficient Funds
POST {{baseUrl}}/transfer
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "senderId": 1,
    "recipientId": 2,
    "amount": 5000
}

### 3. Edge Case: Negative Amount
POST {{baseUrl}}/transfer
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "senderId": 1,
    "recipientId": 2,
    "amount": -50
}

### 4. Edge Case: Same Wallet Transfer
POST {{baseUrl}}/transfer
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "senderId": 1,
    "recipientId": 1,
    "amount": 10
}

### 5. Successful Withdrawal
POST {{baseUrl}}/withdraw
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "walletId": 1,
    "amount": 50
}

### 6. Withdrawal - Insufficient Funds
POST {{baseUrl}}/withdraw
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "walletId": 1,
    "amount": 10000
}

### 7. Withdrawal - Negative Amount
POST {{baseUrl}}/withdraw
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "walletId": 1,
    "amount": -10
}

### 8. Withdrawal - Wallet Not Found
POST {{baseUrl}}/withdraw
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "walletId": 999,
    "amount": 10
}

### 9. Successful Deposit
POST {{baseUrl}}/deposit
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "walletId": 1,
    "amount": 100
}

### 10. Edge Case: Negative Amount
POST {{baseUrl}}/deposit
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "walletId": 1,
    "amount": -50
}

### 11. Edge Case: Wallet Not Found
POST {{baseUrl}}/deposit
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "walletId": 999,
    "amount": 50
}